OL,3,CGirl, 6, suffers serious burns in
OL,4,Cbarbecue fire
OL,6,FA girl, 6, was taken to hospital after
OL,7,Fsuffering serious burns following a
OL,8,Fbarbecue fire in Crawley.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FWorth Road in the town on Sunday (14
OL,12,FJune) following reports that two
OL,13,Fpeople had been injured.
OL,15,FThe girl suffered what police
OL,16,Fdescribed as "serious burns", with a
OL,17,Fman, 38, sustaining "minor burns".
OL,19,FThey were both taken to Kings College
OL,20,FHospital in London so they could
OL,21,Freceive further treatment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
