OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781553961
OL,3,CGirl, 6, suffers serious burns in
OL,4,Cbarbecue fire
OL,6,FIn a statement, Sussex Police said:
OL,7,F"Emergency services attended an
OL,8,Faddress in Worth Road, Crawley on
OL,9,FSunday evening (14 June) after it was
OL,10,Freported that two people had been
OL,11,Finjured in a BBQ fire.
OL,13,F"A 6-year-old girl sustained serious
OL,14,Fburns, and a 38-year-old man also was
OL,15,Finjured, sustaining minor burns. Both
OL,16,Fhave been taken to hospital for
OL,17,Ftreatment.
OL,19,F"Officers attended to support the
OL,20,Femergency response."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
