FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781553961
OL,3,CGirl, 6, suffers serious burns in
OL,4,Cbarbecue fire
OL,6,FSouth East Coast Ambulance added:
OL,7,F"South East Coast Ambulance Service
OL,8,Fwas called to reports of a person in
OL,9,Fneed of medical attention following a
OL,10,Ffire at a property on Worth Road,
OL,11,FCrawley shortly after 19.00 on Sunday,
OL,12,F14 June.
OL,14,F"Ambulance crews were joined at the
OL,15,Fscene by the Air Ambulance Charity
OL,16,FKent, Surrey, Sussex and two patients
OL,17,Fwere assessed and treated at the scene.
OL,19,F"Both patients were taken to King's
OL,20,FCollege Hospital for further
OL,21,Ftreatment."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/3
